---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4">
    <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-4">
      <span class="text-primary-600">安心われかえサービス</span>とは
    </h2>
    <p class="text-gray-500 text-center mb-12">割れ替えのすべてを安心してお任せいただけます</p>

    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 p-8 md:p-12">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8 md:gap-12">
        <!-- Staff photo -->
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-full md:w-auto order-first md:order-last">
          <img
            src={`${base}images/top-img-staff.png`}
            alt="MADOAのスタッフ"
            loading="lazy"
            class="w-full md:w-80 rounded-2xl shadow-lg object-cover"
          />
        </div>

        <!-- Text content -->
        <div class="flex-1 text-center md:text-left">
          <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">
            窓ガラスの割れ替えに特化した専門サービス
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            MADOAの「安心われかえサービス」は、窓ガラスが割れた際の交換作業を、お問い合わせから施工・アフターフォローまで一貫してサポートする専門サービスです。突然のトラブルにも迅速に対応し、お客様の不安を解消します。
          </p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 justify-center md:justify-start">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-green-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 text-white" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">最短即日対応</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 justify-center md:justify-start">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-green-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 text-white" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">明朗会計</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 justify-center md:justify-start">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-green-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 text-white" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">もうすぐ50年</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
